{
  "texts": [
    "We used default hyperparameters for fine-tuning distilBERT.",
    "Last, we intend to test a different classification approach in future work.",
    "Our current model determines what percentage of content in each sentence is internal or external.",
    "In future work, we will finetune a model that classifies individual tokens, while taking into account context from surrounding text.",
    "By operating at the level of individual tokens (roughly equivalent to individual words) rather than at the sentence level, we expect greater accuracy."
  ]
}